{"uuid":"recommended208363","createDate":1563399780000,"customConfigJson":"{\"gameId\":\"208363\",\"readError\":\"false\",\"syncTime\":\"2024-04-30 12:23:53\",\"ratingSummary\":\"推荐\",\"postTime\":\"2019-07-18\",\"gameName\":\"Train Simulator: LNER Class A3 ‘Flying Scotsman’ Loco Add-On\",\"gameLink\":\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/208363\",\"recommendedLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/id/oneness629/recommended/208363/\",\"playTime\":\"0.0\",\"updateTime\":\"2019-07-18\",\"reviewPlayTime\":\"0.0\",\"communityLink\":\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/208363\"}","type":"steamReview","title":"评测 > Train Simulator: LNER Class A3 ‘Flying Scotsman’ Loco Add-On","content":"<div id=\"ReviewText\">\n 模拟火车 Class A3 飞翔的苏格兰人 现代版 DLC\n <br>\n ~一台创造各种世界纪录的蒸汽机车~\n <br>\n 别小看它，它可是可以上100mph的蒸汽车~\n <br>\n （虽然我的技术开不到那个速度~真的~）\n <br>\n 蒸汽车游玩难度很高~如果不会开~可以看看我的蒸汽车指南~虽然也只是简单入门~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1593543952\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_0\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1593543952</a>\n <br>\n <br>\n 有一个职业任务，可惜场景是现代场景。\n <br>\n And 有告警系统，不按时按HUD上的警告按钮会紧急制动。\n <br>\n ~Emmm~蒸汽车哪有这么高级的东西喔~\n <br>\n <br>\n And 场景是现代场景，你说周围都是烧油的和电动的列车经过，就自己是烧煤的蒸汽车~emmm~而且周边都是高楼大厦~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1807738387\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_1\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1807738387</a>\n <br>\n And 场景是夜晚，黑灯瞎火的~也不好截图~emm~\n <br>\n And 那个前车灯简直是摆设~一点都不亮~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1807738602\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" id=\"dynamiclink_2\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1807738602</a>\n <br>\n And 驾驶舱连个灯都没~\n <br>\n 不过蒸汽车的汽笛确实比大部分电力机车和燃油机车好听~\n <br>\n <br>\n 最后~在终点站~你能看到蒸汽车、柴油机车、电力机车3种类别~在一起ing~\n <br><a class=\"bb_link\" href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1807738814\" target